column2: ggplotly(ggplot(data[,list("avgNO2"=mean(no2)),by=c("year","month","state")],aes(x=as.factor(month),y=avgNO2,fill=as.factor(month),group=1))+geom_bar(stat = "identity")+facet_wrap(~as.factor(state))+labs(title = "Average No2 level in states by months",x="Months", y = "Average So2 value",fill="months")+theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5,face = "bold",color = "black")))
